          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " research showing that the current federal minimum wage of $7.25 is worth less today than it’s ever been.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This abominable reality could continue for the foreseeable future if Harris now refuses to use her power to add a minimum wage increase to what could be the only piece of major legislation that could move in a gridlocked Senate.",
            "type": "text",
